<speak version=&quot;1.0&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis&quot; xml:lang=&quot;en-IN&quot;><voice name=&quot;en-IN-Diya:DragonHDLatestNeural&quot; parameters=&quot;temperature=0.7;enhancePronunciation=true&quot;><p><s>Hello, Deepti. This is the plain pronunciation.</s><break time=&quot;500ms&quot;/><s>Hello, <sub alias=&quot;Deep-tee&quot;>Deepti</sub>. This uses an alias pronunciation.</s><break time=&quot;500ms&quot;/><s>Hello, <phoneme alphabet=&quot;ipa&quot; ph=&quot;diːpti&quot;>Deepti</phoneme>. This uses phonetic guidance.</s><break time=&quot;700ms&quot;/><s>Deepti, we are going to follow one financial idea from the real-world problem that created the need for it, through the mechanism, and into the decision it changes.</s></p></voice></speak>